Multi-Currency Solutions
Providing solutions that allow banks and their merchants to offer customers personalized payments in their home currency – at the point of sale, online or at the ATM.








Payment Processing
Offering international payment, transaction and multi-currency processing services that allow acquirers and processors to quickly enter new markets and expand payment acceptance around the world.








Gateway Solutions
Facilitating Global eCommerce through our PCI compliant international payment platform.











The Better Way to Pay®
International customers enjoy the confidence and convenience of paying in the currency they know best – their own! Find out how Pay in Your Currency® can help merchants reduce the cost of foreign card processing while providing superior customer service to international customers.  
Learn More





















































Offer international customers the choice to pay in the currency they know best – their own.






Provide international travelers with the convenience of knowing, at the time of ATM withdrawal, the exact amount debited from their bank account in their own currency.






Convert international browsers into buyers by pricing in multiple currencies online.













