			Company Description 


			Planet Payment, Inc. provides international payment, transaction and multi-currency processing services. The company offers banks and their merchants with innovative services to accept, process and reconcile electronic payments and its point of sale multi-currency payment processing services are des...
		


                Planet Payment, Inc. provides international payment, transaction and multi-currency processing services. The company offers banks and their merchants with innovative services to accept, process and reconcile electronic payments and its point of sale multi-currency payment processing services are designed for merchants in retail, restaurant and hospitality environments. It operates its business through the following segments: Multi-currency processing services and Payment processing services. The Multi-currency processing services segment comprise solutions designed to enable acquiring banks, processors and merchants to respond to these challenges by integrating its secure and reliable processing platform into their existing systems. The Payment processing services segment provides services for merchants in the retail, restaurant, and hospitality environments. Planet Payment was founded by Philip D. Beck on October 12, 1999 and is headquartered in Long Beach, NY.
            




