Planet Payment Stock Sees Short Interest Decrease By 16.6%
The most recent short interest data has been released for the 07/29/2016 settlement date, which shows a 254,423 share decrease in total short interest for Planet Payment Incorporated , to 1,277,911, a decrease of 16.60% since 07/15/2016. Total short interest is just one way to look at short data; another metric that we here at Dividend Channel find particularly useful is the "days to cover" metric because it considers both the total shares short and the average daily volume of shares traded.

